<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Mi Ruta SJR – Olvidé mi contraseña</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-sRIl4kxILFvY47J16cr9ZwB07vP4J8+LH7qKQnuqkuIAvNWLzeN8tE5YBujZqJLB" crossorigin="anonymous">
  <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/image/favicon.ico">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito:wght@400;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --green: #2DC653;
      --green-dark: #22A845;
      --green-light: #E8F9ED;
      --green-bg2: #1E9E3F;
      --yellow: #FFC107;
      --gray-light: #F4F4F4;
      --gray-border: #E0E0E0;
      --text-dark: #1A1A1A;
      --text-mid: #555;
      --text-soft: #999;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
      background-color: var(--green);
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      position: relative;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    /* ── FOOTER ── */
    footer {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      color: #fff !important;
    }
    footer h6, footer p { color: #fff !important; }
    footer a { color: #fff !important; opacity: 0.85; }
    footer a:hover { opacity: 1; }

    /* Decorative blobs */
    .blob1 {
      position: fixed;
      top: -80px; right: -80px;
      width: 320px; height: 320px;
      background: var(--green-bg2);
      border-radius: 50%;
      opacity: 0.5;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 0;
    }
    .blob2 {
      position: fixed;
      bottom: -100px; left: -60px;
      width: 280px; height: 280px;
      background: var(--green-bg2);
      border-radius: 50%;
      opacity: 0.4;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    /* ── CARD WRAPPER ── */
    .page-content {
      flex: 1;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 40px 16px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .card {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 28px;
      padding: 44px 40px 36px;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 390px;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.14);
      animation: fadeUp .5s ease both;
    }
    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); }
      to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    /* ── LOGO ── */
    .logo-row {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    .logo-row .bus-icon {
      width: 40px; height: 40px;
      background: var(--green);
      border-radius: 10px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 22px;
    }
    .logo-row .brand-text {
      font-size: 17px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--text-dark);
    }
    .logo-row .brand-text span { color: var(--yellow); }

    /* ── ICON CIRCLE ── */
    .icon-circle {
      width: 64px; height: 64px;
      background: var(--green-light);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      margin: 0 auto 20px;
    }
    .icon-circle svg { width: 30px; height: 30px; }

    /* ── HEADINGS ── */
    h1 {
      font-size: 26px;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: var(--text-dark);
      text-align: center;
      line-height: 1.25;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .subtitle {
      font-size: 13.5px;
      color: var(--text-soft);
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    /* ── STEPS ── */
    .steps {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    .step {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 4px;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text-soft);
    }
    .step.active { color: var(--yellow); }
    .step .dot {
      width: 28px; height: 28px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--gray-light);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--text-soft);
    }
    .step.active .dot { background: var(--yellow); color: #fff; }
    .step-line {
      width: 32px;
      height: 2px;
      background: var(--gray-border);
      align-self: center;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      position: relative;
      top: -10px;
    }

    /* ── FORM ── */
    .field-label {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text-dark);
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      display: block;
    }
    .input-wrap {
      position: relative;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .input-wrap .icon {
      position: absolute;
      left: 14px;
      top: 50%;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      color: #bbb;
    }
    .input-wrap input {
      width: 100%;
      height: 50px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      border: 1.5px solid var(--gray-border);
      background: var(--gray-light);
      padding: 0 16px 0 42px;
      font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--text-dark);
      outline: none;
      transition: border-color .2s, background .2s;
    }
    .input-wrap input:focus {
      border-color: var(--green);
      background: #fff;
    }
    .input-wrap input::placeholder { color: #bbb; }

    /* ── PRIMARY BUTTON ── */
    .btn-primary-custom {
      width: 100%;
      height: 50px;
      background: var(--green);
      border: none;
      border-radius: 14px;
      color: #fff;
      font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 800;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background .2s, transform .1s;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .btn-primary-custom:hover  { background: var(--green-dark); }
    .btn-primary-custom:active { transform: scale(.98); }

    /* ── BACK LINK ── */
    .back-link {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 6px;
      font-size: 13.5px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text-soft);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color .2s;
    }
    .back-link:hover { color: var(--green-dark); }
    .back-link svg { width: 14px; height: 14px; }

    /* ── DIVIDER ── */
    .divider {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      margin: 4px 0 16px;
      color: var(--text-soft);
      font-size: 12px;
    }
    .divider::before, .divider::after {
      content: '';
      flex: 1;
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--gray-border);
    }

    /* ── INFO BOX ── */
    .info-box {
      background: var(--green-light);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 12px 14px;
      font-size: 12.5px;
      color: var(--green-dark);
      font-weight: 600;
      display: flex;
      gap: 8px;
      align-items: flex-start;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .info-box svg { flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }
    footer {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="blob1"></div>
  <div class="blob2"></div>

  <%- include("templates/navbar.ejs", {titulo: "Olvidar contraseña" })%>

  <div class="page-content">
    <div class="card">

      <div class="logo-row">
        <!-- <div class="bus-icon">🚌</div> -->
        <div class="brand-text">Mi Ruta <span>SJR</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="icon-circle">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#2DC653" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <circle cx="8" cy="15" r="4"/>
          <path d="M12 11l8-8"/>
          <path d="M20 3l1 1-3 3-1-1"/>
          <path d="M18 7l1 1"/>
        </svg>
      </div>

      <h1>¿Olvidaste tu<br/>contraseña?</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Ingresa tu correo y te enviaremos<br/>un enlace para restablecerla.</p>

      <div class="steps">
        <div class="step active">
          <div class="dot">1</div>
          <span>Correo</span>
        </div>
        <div class="step-line"></div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="dot">2</div>
          <span>Enlace</span>
        </div>
        <div class="step-line"></div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="dot">3</div>
          <span>Nueva clave</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="info-box">
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#22A845" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
          <path d="M12 16v-4M12 8h.01"/>
        </svg>
        Recibirás un correo en menos de 5 minutos. Revisa también tu carpeta de spam.
      </div>

      <label class="field-label" for="email">Correo electrónico</label>
      <div class="input-wrap">
        <span class="icon">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#bbb" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="16" rx="3"/>
            <path d="M2 7l10 7 10-7"/>
          </svg>
        </span>
        <input type="email" id="email" placeholder="tucorreo@ejemplo.com" />
      </div>

      <button class="btn-primary-custom">Enviar enlace de recuperación</button>

      <div class="divider">o</div>

      <a class="back-link" href="/login">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M19 12H5M12 5l-7 7 7 7"/>
        </svg>
        Volver a Iniciar sesión
      </a>

    </div>
  </div>
  
  <footer class="p-3 mb-2 bg-transparent text-white">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <p class="mb-1 text-dark">© 2025 Mi Ruta SJR</p>
      <a href="/terminos" class="text-secondary text-decoration-none mx-2">Términos</a> |
      <a href="/privacidad" class="text-secondary text-decoration-none mx-2">Privacidad</a> |
      <a href="/faq" class="text-secondary text-decoration-none mx-2">FAQ</a>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
